---
title: Prawn & Leek Risotto with Basil Pesto & Garlic Pangrattato
description: A prawn risotto, that sounds like the magic words to conjure one enchanted dinner, fresh and steaming from the oven. Be amazed by the garlicky pangrattato on top of the prawns with pops of leek and herbs scattered throughout. Your tastebuds will be in awe.
